   * <ul>
   * <li>Overrides of JavaBean property getters of the test class.
   * (ie. override {@link Configuration#getWebDriver()})
   * </li>
   * <li>JavaBean property setters of the test class.
   * (ie. call {@link Configuration#setWebDriver(String)})
